00:28.245 --> 00:30.639
♪ DON'T YOU WORRY

00:31.379 --> 00:34.034
♪ IT'S GONNA BE ALL RIGHT ♪

00:36.775 --> 00:38.647
♪ CAUSE I'M ALWAYS READY

